{"word":"ἀντιόομαι","slug":"ἀντιόομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀντιόομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀντίος'><el>ἀντίος</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to resist, oppose</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:— <el>οἱ ἀντιούμενοι  οἱ ἐναντίοι</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, once in <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}